description:
Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers 1,422 sq. ft. of thoughtfully designed living space that seamlessly blends modern elegance with everyday comfort. From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by the glow of polished porcelain tile floors throughout, an inviting open floor plan, and the perfect split-bedroom layout that offers both privacy and space.The heart of this home is its completely remodeled kitchen, featuring all-new cabinets, sleek quartzite countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The island boasts a drawer microwave, drop-down pendant lighting, and ample space for meal prep and casual dining--perfect for entertaining family and friends.  Every bedroom includes spacious walk-in closets, while impact doors and windows offer both safety and peace of mind. The newly paved gray brick driveway, along with matching pavers on the pool deck and patio, create a polished and sophisticated outdoor space. The private backyard, complete with a covered patio, is ideal for outdoor dining or simply enjoying a serene evening by the pool.
   This home has been freshly landscaped with new sod, providing great curb appeal, while the large two-car garage and dedicated laundry/utility room offer extra convenience and storage.
   Located in the heart of Boca Raton, this property offers the ultimate lifestyle with no HOA. You'll be within walking distance of Town Center Mall, Pine Crest School, and University Woodlands Park. Enjoy easy access to I-95 and the Turnpike, along with top-rated public schools and close proximity to FAU and Lynn University. Take advantage of the nearby world-class dining, shopping, and entertainment options at Mizner Park and Downtown Boca, or unwind with just a short drive to the beach.
   This is more than a houseit's a place where memories are made and dreams come true. Ready to call it home? Schedule your tour today and start your next chapter in this beautifully updated and perfectly located residence!
